garrys modabbreviated gmod is a really really really really open sandbox game garrys mod provides its players with all of the tools to practically do whatever the heck they want when the want to do it in garrys mod you may either choose to play singleplayer and screw around with things or you may play the multiplayer of the game and participate in one of to 100 gametypes to choose from these gamemodes themselves also provide plenty of servers for you to choose from in the sandbox gametype alone the servers can range from being a simple peaceful environments where players can gracefully construct whatever their hearts may desire without harm being brought upon them  to a sandbox server with frequent violent occursions while some players are building  to an extremely hecktic sandbox server where players are fighting for their own lives to even try to build in the innovative darkrp gametype you have servers that can range from realistic goodsporty experiences  to a serious roleplay server where gangsters cower away from the patrolling police instead of jumping out like freaking lunatics  to darkrp servers with very frequent unjustified shootouts random deathmatching spawnkilling and propkilling  to roleplay servers where there is a perfect blend of chaos and serious roleplay  to half life 2 roleplaying servers in which you try to roleplay as a citizen during the combine oppressionthis actually has its own gametype clockwork  to other roleplay servers that include vicious mindless bloodthirsty zombies that come out to try and murder you while you attempt to properly roleplay in a wasteland environment there are also other popular gamemodes such as jailbreak flood zombie survival trouble in terrorist townttt deathrun and prophunt just lying out there waiting for you to join right in and participate in the uniquely fun experiences that each of them has to offer dont think that garrys mod would be a waste of your $10will be less on steam sales because garrys mod will provide you with enough gaming entertainment to last you up to several years the only issue about garrys mod is that some maps in the gamemost of the maps are customly created by players along with some weaponsm9k is a popular custom weapons pack entities snpcsscriptednonplayercharacters or ai that are customly made and vehiclesscars is a popular custom vehicle pack require you to own csscounter strike source httpstoresteampoweredcomapp240 dodsday of defeat source httpstoresteampoweredcomapp300 hl2ep1half life 2 episode 1 httpstoresteampoweredcomapp380 hl2ep2half life 2 episode 2 httpstoresteampoweredcomapp420 tf2team fortress 2 httpstoresteampoweredcomapp440 portal httpstoresteampoweredcomapp400 and portal 2 httpstoresteampoweredcomapp620  in order to see the textures of the corresponding custom files you may still be able to download the textures from these games from the internet without actually purchasing the game itself however all of that mess aside garrys mod is definitely worth your $10 if not even more this game will offer limitless entertainment to just about any age groupsbut please no 8 year olds you will have the world of physics at your fingertips if you purchase this game and that world will be worth everything you put into it it offers you the freedom of using your imagination in order to do whatever the heck you want when you want to do it and all you have to know how to do to make that happen is  well  to know how to do it
