what is everyones favorite source sandbox game while garrys mod of course as the name suggests garrys mod was orignially a mod and still is  in some regards the mod was originally created by garry newman with not much more help than the source sdk once the mod reached a certain point of interest among the players so did it over att valve being that valve is very good at taking modmakers under their wings and helping them to reach its full potential  for a cut of the cake of course therefore valve naturally became the publisher of garrys mod and the game could remain the rights and to accumulate profit profit unlike some other notoriginallyvalveprojects such as counterstrike portal and left 4 dead garrys mod actually got to remain an indie game somewhere around here garry founded facepunch studios and released an actual game  garrys mod 10 this time they could charge money for the mod as valve was getting a share of the sales income the game has always been pretty cheap and has been on steam sales at least a billion times so everyone and their cats have this game rightfully so if you have other source games on your steam account you can link them and add some of its content into garrys mod giving even more stuff to balls around with garrys mod is the perfect game if you want to kind of pretend to be a game designer and just play around with the source engine which is an awesome engine for this i might add build your dream dollhouse featuring all your favorite source characters tank gordon freeman terrorist demoman gman etc then blow them into pieces garrys mod 11 a recent free update added even more stuff to the game you can do endless stuff in this game you might want to look up som tutorials or guides on how to use all the different tools and such i never got too deep into garrys mod i dipped my toes in the water and tried the basic stuff everything from just flooding the place with npc to building airborne vehicles i am always amazed about the sheer amount you can do in this game but i will probably never get there myself i am hoping that this game will move on live to see source 2 and to get more stuff ported over to it everyone likes sandbox games you already have this game so why are you still reading go play
