ine 12 gangsters raiding the pd without a mob boss theyre like playing cod source heh now for ttt while better than darkrp itself and the good concept some players will just rdm to know whos the traitor then if one innocent kills the traitor another innocent kills the guy who killed the traitor wasent that obvious minges yep minges are a common species of the gmod world mostly kids and angry idiots who want to play gmod his own way instead of playing the game that the server wants mainly in online sandbox ttt and darkrp also they have the fact that they will not stop until they say you stop because theyre butthurt and they dont even know how to play useless  in workshop nearly 90% of the stuff is almost useless and stolen from the original creators while 10% if it is good stuff the 90% of it was useless dupes saves and stolen addons if you want to get the good stuff then dont get the useless stuff these are my opinions about gmod but i will still recommend this because i love making screenies and hanging out with other players but my rating wouldnt make you happy here it is pros you can do what you want in sandbox good for making videos that you want less time 23 gamemodes are almost good cons workshop is now invaded by useless and stolen stuff kids and minges tend to ruin the fun darkrp killed the game requires a another source game for extra content overall score 78100
