there are so many game types people have created in garrys mod that its impossible to not find something you like there are 3 game modes i currently play and those are trouble in terrorist town prop hunt and murder keep in mind there are tons more but those are the ones i have tried so when someone first got me this game i thought it was a boring sandbox game until this same friend of mine told me that the sandbox is just one little feature there are mods within the mod let me explain trouble in terrorist town ttt because it is an incredibly popular mode in ttt youve got three types of people you can be per round randomly chosen innocent traitor or detective as an innocent you walk around the map with chosen gun that you can pick up from the ground when you spawn there are all kinds of weapons your goal is to not die and find the traitors you cannot kill people randomly without proof that they have done something wrong you can shoot them if they start shooting at you for example or you catch them in the act of shooting someone else its a very social game so you would announce to the lobby to kill this person on sight as they are shooting at me also known as a kos on their player name they are also a traitor if you see them using an item or weapon that regular innocents do not have access to like knives c4 silenced awp silenced pistol and automatic among other things if you kill a traitor you would know if you identified the body of the person you shot which you should always do as an innocent if you came across a dead body you can then say you are proven see the rest of the lobby doesnt know you are innocent you are just as suspiscious as anyone else so on to traitors long story short kill everyone except fellow traitors you can buy special weapons and items like radar to help you using in game credits achieved from killing innocents dont get caught or else the whole lobby is out to get you and that makes winning quite hard on your part sniping helps disguises help and planting c4 explosives when noone is around gives you an advantage being a traitor involves being sly dont be too quiet in game people may think youre a traitor try to change the story a silver tongue will help you ok detectives you are an innocent with more poweryou can get dna off dead bodies to find traitors you can buy health stations radar ammo silenced awp and the like your job is to track the traitors down and thats about it different servers have different things for their ttt but thats just one of the amazing things about this game
