well what can i say about this game its extremely cheap at just over five pounds and is often reduced down to 2 pounds in steam sales but even the default price is reasonable when you compare it to the price of most modern console games also is a game that doesnt require a super beefy pc with an expensive graphics card or cpu to run at a decent framerate i played most of my hours on it on my 6 year old toshiba laptop thats not even meant for gaming and only recently upgraded to a gaming pc to play other games it enables you to use maps textures weapons characters and pretty much anything from other games compatible with it such as left 4 dead 2 counter strikesource and other very popular games such as a free to play game called team fortress 2 tf2 with this feature built into the game it enables you to explore maps create spawn npc`s non playable characters vehicles and pretty much anything else your head can think of i have played gmod for nearly 200 hours and i can definitely say that i would recommend this game to a friend as well as tf2 and as a matter of fact i ended up buying this game because one of my friends suggested it to me to play
