what is garrys mod garrys mod is a hard thing to describe you could say its another communitymade mod to source that was approved by valve or you could say its a pure incarnation of the internet and all its current shenanigans whichever works start up the game and youll immediately notice a lot and i mean a lot  of pink and black squares this is the placeholder texture for all missing textures you dont have to fix this either buy the game counterstrike source or download its textures which are completely free and legal to obtain just make sure you get them from a trusted website on to the actual review garrys mod is anything you can build and everything you can imagine it is the ultimate sandbox experience you can create contraptions and test them out in singleplayer or have the most fun you can have online tf2 reference p and play around with your buddies dont have buddies garrys mod has those too there are loads of gamemodes to choose from ttt prophunt and darkrp being the most popular you can even make them yourself want to make a my little pony roleplay gamemode do it  want to create your own community addicted to cars do it want to invite some friends to a server and eat some virtual cake do it you really cant cram what garrys mod is into one review but to basically sum it up you can eat balls to gain health 1010
