garrys mod is often regarded as the most historically relevant electronic weapon in the history of the world garrys mod runs on a nextnextgen super engine often refered to as the source engine and was outlawed until the second canadian civil war in which it was used by the canadian freedom fighters against the canadian fascist legion in retaliation to their halflife 2 source weapon garrys mod not only uses all assets from halflife 2 but combines those of other source weapons used by seperate unrelated organizations including counterstrike source used by terrorists in the middle east and team fortress 2 popular among mercenaries intertnationally using each weapon to their advantage the canadian fascist legion was inevitably defeated and the canadian freedom fighters next attempted to dispose of garrys mod soon however they found that garrys mod had not only acheived sentience but was spreading through the internet at an alarming rate what surprised the freedom fighters even more than this was that garrys mod wasnt destructive at all on the contrary it soon turned itself into a stable and usable program similar in style to that of a video game the video game company valve took notice and soon released garrys mod on its online gaming platform steam after the extreme success of garrys mod valve made stable versions of all source weapons and released them as video games on steam quinn matthew  major modern wars and advances 20202056 the history of the world new york muenster publishing 2056 337 print
