okay so my last review was short so heres a longer more detailed version when it comes to sandboxes nothing beats garrys mod content garrys mod has a huge variety of content even without the workshop items the amount of stuff you can make depends on how much you have youre armed with the usual set of halflife 2 weaponsalong with a few legit gmod stuff the physgun the camera and a tool gun it already comes with one of the halflife 2 episodes and thats a bonus not happy with the usual source ragdolls you can get some nonsource ragdolls via the workshop cause theres even more stuff at the workshop sonic minecraft and mario stuff you can also change your player model using the context menu gameplay as i said before youre equipped with hl2 weapons exceptions are physgun camera and toolgun you can do anything you want whether its catapulting a ragdoll from left 4 dead 2 or facing a wave of combine soldiers from halflife 2 you can also spawn props and such and make a neat movie just be aware of what youre doing your imagination is the limit concerns & problems hold on a sec dont buy it yet as there is some problems with thisthis may be an excellent game but there is some concerns one being that there is way too many dupes i mean look up terraria in the workshop and as you can see there is alot of demon eyes eye of cthulhus and twins and  and nothing of a real addon cant they do us a favor create a minecraftish sprite of terraria items at the very least but if youre making a movie then this problem is easily solvable with a little sony vegas another concern is that not everything you might like is on the workshop ie i looked up roblox on the workshop and like terraria pure dupes the only real addon is a somewhat glitchy npc and when i type in something thatll get it to walk right it really slows my pc down another example would be that the super monkey ball ragdolls do not support the bone merger tool theyre a little small i that i might understand but it would be nice if they too could be in the hatwearing buisness the most serious thing you might wanna know too is that this game relies heavily on source games you wont have louis having his pills on gmod without left 4 dead 2 nor have gordon freeman without one of the halflife 2 games a screenshot example of what happens when you dont have counter strike source can be seen here httpsteamcommunitycomsharedfilesfiledetailsid268005543 so before getting the game make sure you have the nessecary amount of games that use the source engine here is the priority of what games you might need in my point of view 1 as many halflife games as possible 2 counter strike probably any but peferrably source 3 left 4 dead 2 4 portal 5 team fortress 2 and etc the reason i put tf2 on 5 is because that its free so there is little need to have that asap but then again if youre planning to use tf2 ragdolls most of the time then that makes sense just remember that this my opinion so your priorities may vary final thoughts garrys mod offers alot of content for you to play around with but if you dont have many source games then it could be a problem but if you dont plan on using so many things then again if youre a guy looking to mess around with stuff or feeling creative then this is your opportunity the cost is well worth it especially since that im writing this during the steam summer sale 2014 but really the amount you should shell out varies on how many source games you have how often are you gonna play with it and how good is your imagination and creativity for example if you only have tf2 but dont plan on playing gmod often due to your lack of imagination and creativity then dont buy it without a really cheap price but if you have css hl2 and l4d2 and really wanna see what you can do and do plan on playing it for a huge time pattern then yes it is worth full price so the verdict is in garrys mod not sucks  810 happy ragdolls here
