as someone who has played a ton of this game i thought id write a simple review on it first things first if you have fun friends this game will never ever get boring that being said play this with friends there is an endless amount of content on the workshop which makes this game entertaining not even counting the immense amount of multiplayer game modes even without friends multiplayer can be somewhat entertaining next id like to point out that if you get this game you are going to definitely need counter strike source the next priorities would be half life episode 1 and episode 2 thought those 2 are not required the last thing id like to touch is addons they can be fun but they can ruin your experience if you have a terrible computer and get 300 addons you will have low hard drive space and probably 10minutes loading your game every time that being said dont just download everything you want think will you actually use it a lot all in all you will not get bored of garrys mod there is simply to much to do
