this game is amazing for everyone the is due to the fact that you can get almost any gamemode you want on gmod the amount of devs out there makes this game amazing as well new workshop content everyday and new gamemodes everyday the community is just generally amazing on this game the game has many bugs but these bugs affect some people not all they are normally visual bugs or crashes these can usually be sorted though and if there is a game changinglimiting bug facepunch fix it quick enough for you to get playing or you can probably find one of the many possible solutions online the graphics on this game are decent and for obvious reasons halflife fans will love them they are modern graphics but not as uptodate as a game like gta v but this is to be expected from a now older game in conclusion this game is decent for the price the major downfall is the probability of a bug limiting your experience but this is not very likely i would recommend getting this game if you are looking for halflife online with other ways of playing
