my gmod story it started out when i joined a small freebuild server no new things just old nice addonsnothing special i built myself a small cottage which looked more like a hobos den i went to my neighbors house he was making a fancy old graveyard with a small pumpkin guy behind it i asked hey what are you making today he responded with a short grunt over the mic i asked again please do tell another grunt i soon gave up i noticed a small gaurd holding a rifle i asked my neighbor who is that another grunt i was tired of it so i went back to my house to improve chapter 2 wow i wonder how i did it i had a fullnicecottage a admin walked up and asked where ya get them skills mate i responded with wasnt hard i just studied his graveyard the admin walked over to the graveyard well well nice job mind ya shinin light on yur builds this time he responded no sir he showed him how to build a fancy house i then settled into my cottage and fell asleep chapter 3 i woke up the next game the fog was turned up so i checked my settings no fog though i went to the admin to ask what is with this fog he simply said i dont know we found a small crowd near a kiosk a melon kiosk i looked around my neighbor was their with the gaurd buying some melons crraaacck a 9mm goes off i ran to my house oh dear i heard more and then a loud slump as the kiosk fell a admin started banging begging to be let in i heard more crossbows and 9mms go off it was all we could get our hands on i grabbed my 9mm and slowly opened the door the adminand a player rushed in blockading the door and windows he yelled upstairs guys uistars or theu ger us his message was full of grammar mistakesbecause of his worry we blockaded the steps creeeaak a door opens a loud smash and then a groan a players head shoots upstairs oh no says the admin he continues to barricade the stairwell while me and the player are in my rather cramped attic craaash my lamp falls i hear the admin yelp in pain then a large amount of banging it stops and i hear a bloodcurdling scream the head shoots up into the attic i hear the creature break a windowthen into the attic me and the player here run another bang as i hide behind furniture the player hides behind a broken wood fence i see a apelike shape with a bloody mouth and a stained fur coat i then see the player across from me freeze and fall to the ground he is paralyzedand i cant help him the monster jumps downboy oh boy i got a good view on em he graps the player rips off his head and pulls out his spine the creature then proceeds to knaw on the spinethen throws the head off into the fog i then also see him creep up behind another player moving inside who is armed with a 9mm and a lantern i run out the windowand also catch a glimpse of his mighty pounce i hear another scream as he rips out his spine to chew on then i run to the broken melon stand only to see the last of the players leaving the server threw the underground subwaya ingame addon that allows travel threw servers i missed it i see the last station close its just me now chapter 4 finale  i then realise i could have left but when i try toi cant the creature is near a sudden thump as a evac server pops up[fastdl]evaccrashcourse[evacforcrashes] i quickly hop onto never join that server again
