this game is full of suprises from its vast variety of fun messing around gamemodes like sandbox or cinema to the more serious and political darkrp and trouble in terroist town to the many addons being created in the workshop everyday what makes this game even better is that everything is created by others in the community  hence the name mod prophunt ttt darkrp murder deathrun are just some of the game modes i got addicted to if youre in the right servers the amount of fun you can have is insane then if you get a server running with some friends you could play some sandbox and download many of the thousands of mods available right at your reach i recommend the m9k weapon packs and nuke packs so much death >d the only major problem is textures counterstrike source and half life 2 are required for the game otherwise almost all props and textures will be either a huge error or a pink and black chequred material this can be easily fixed by downloading the textures themselves if you dont have the games but it can be quite a hassle there can also be textures from other games needed like hl ep1 or 2 or even some nonvalve games like mass effect 3 overall you can have a lot of fun with this game with or without friends online or offline well worth the small price if i was to rate this game id give it a 95 for its versitility and wide range of ways to play i definately recommend it for any hardcore or even casual gamer
