garrys mod gm is a virtual world developed by linden lab launched on june 23 2003 and is accessible on the internet a free client program called the viewer enables its users called residents to interact with each other through avatars residents can explore meet other residents socialize participate in individual and group activities and create and trade virtual property and services with one another or travel throughout the world which residents refer to as the grid garrys mod is for people aged 18 and over
