okay there are many pros and cons to garrys mod with the cons in my opinion far outweighing the pros however this could be biased as my rig isnt exactly the best around but despite the huge amount of negativity that may or may not be present here m80s it really all comes down to what you enjoy the most out of a videogame and since this is a multiplayer sandboxtype game chances are youre probably going to like it one way or the other so lets get started shall we like i said garrys mod is a single playermultiplayer sandbox game that allows you to do just about anything provided you know how to code in luaalthough not really needed to enjoy the gameand have an outstanding amount of patience ill get into this eventually and features many gamemodes that are sure to provide you with hours of fun ttt im looking at you <3 along with gamemodes garrys mod has a huge modding community the steam community workshop provides some pretty in great addons for you to use in your creations or for your amusement in singleplayer of course this is where  gets real and damnright annoying alright if youve read this far youll know i mentioned something along the lines of lua that my friend is the games coding language just about every addon such as custom weapons vehicles and generally any script that is supposed to make anything happen really is coded using lua and boy is it tedious to get more than 60 addons working the thing that bugs me the most out of this is that most mod authors dont tell you what other addons their mods are compatible with which results in lua errors that will eventually lead to you losing your precious sanity seriously i lost count of the many times ive crashed because of too many addons or memory loss the memory loss is my fault really yay 32bit windows so getting over 60 addons is tedious right now on to the community huge modding community sure but the online community is ing terrible all im going to tell you is that you should make use of the mute button whenever possible i see too many players online pointlessly complaining about someones voice when they could just make use of the mute button i know that most of the time these guys know there is a way to mute people but some people genuinely dont and ive no clue as to why all in all its not that bad of a game if you can manage to ignore these problems that for some reason have not been looked into yet in garry man
