huhcant believe i havent written a review on this game yet well here it goes garrys mod is a physics sandbox unlike regular games there arent any predefined aims or goals you are given the tools and leave you to play you spawn objects and weld them together to create your own contraptions  whether thats a car a rocket a catapult or something that doesnt have a name yet  thats up to you if youre not too great at construction  dont worry you can place a variety of characters in silly positions there are also a large variety of game modes as well like trouble in terrorist town where there are innocent terrorists and traitor terrorists the traitor must kill all the innocents before the innocents find out who the traitor is stop slender where players are to roam around a map collecting eight pages but there is one player who takes control of slenderman his goal is to kill everyone looking for pages there are a whole variety of gamemodes but itll take me forever to go through them all garrys mod is a fun sandbox game which allows you to do and construct whatever you like heres a score for what i think 910 now excuse me i need to construct my top secret scientific titanium plated rocket ship ps this game includes thousands of mods for your enjoyment hence garrys mod
