garrys mod is a creative singleplayer and multiplayer sandbox game you can do a lot of things from making fantastic working machines to just having fun by posing ragdolls around what i really love about garrys mod is that you can download over 150000 mods weapons ragdolls skins maps the list goes on and on when you start garrys mod you can either do singleplayer where you can choose a map to be in and make stuff and do a ton of other things or you can do multiplayer where you can grab a few of your friends and play on a sandbox server and have fun together or you can find new friends and go play prop hunt or trouble in terrorist town or a lot of other game modes i would recommend this game to pretty much every creative person or even people who just want to blow stuff up there is so much to do on garrys mod that you wont run out of things to do theres constantly new addons to get well i hope this review helps you choose whether or not you want to get this game or not if you find this review helpful please leave a thumbs up
